Hi {!Lead.FirstName},

Thank you for the great conversation with our instructor. We'd like to move you forward to one more interview. This one is with our Case Manager.

This conversation is about 30 minutes. The focus is making sure we can set you up for success in the program. We'll talk through any barriers or supports you may need. That includes transportation, childcare, scheduling, or technology, and how ULEM can help.

Book your case manager interview: https://go.ulem.org/rts-book-casemanager

Interviews are conducted via Zoom or in person at ULEM Boston, 88 Warren Street, Roxbury, MA 02119. Please book your slot within the next 5 business days.

After this interview, our team will make a final decision and be in touch shortly.

The RTS Team at ULEM
